   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promote increased awareness on social protection among key stakeholders - Uganda National NGO Forum (UNNGO) workshops.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The grant has four deliverable actions: 1. Produce a Workshop Report 2. Provision of a brief process report with new learning&apos;s and or recommendations for the future. 3. Provision of a list of identified Social Protection Champions 4. Provision of full accountability requirements within 7 days after the event.</narrative>
